---
title: Broccoli-Kale Caesar with Chicken plus Garlic Bread & Parmesan
description: Our crunchy broccoli slaw blend is the hero ingredient that gets this quick chicken meal on the table in a lightning-fast 20 minutes! You’ll toss the veggies with creamy Caesar dressing, top with tender, garlicky seared chicken cutlets, and finish with a sprinkle of Parmesan cheese and a side of chewy-crisp ciabatta garlic bread.
